---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Use">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl mb-8">Terms of Use</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong class="text-ink">Effective date:</strong> March 28, 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink pt-4">1. Acceptance</h2>
      <p>By using Irregular Pearl you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the platform.</p>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink pt-4">2. What Irregular Pearl is</h2>
      <p>Irregular Pearl is a non-profit, community-driven platform for classical music knowledge. We provide structured information about musical works, editions, and recordings, along with community discussion spaces for musicians.</p>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink pt-4">3. User accounts</h2>
      <p>You may browse Irregular Pearl without an account. To post discussions, rate editions, or mark pieces you're working on, you need to sign in via Google OAuth. You are responsible for your account activity.</p>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink pt-4">4. User content</h2>
      <p>When you post discussions or reviews, you grant Irregular Pearl a non-exclusive, royalty-free license to display that content on the platform. You retain ownership of your content. You may delete your own posts at any time.</p>
      <p>Do not post content that infringes copyright, is abusive, or violates any law. We reserve the right to remove content that violates these terms.</p>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink pt-4">5. Edition and piece data</h2>
      <p>Edition metadata (publisher, editor, year) is factual information. Descriptions are written by Irregular Pearl contributors and staff. External links point to third-party sites (IMSLP, YouTube, Wikipedia) that we do not control.</p>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink pt-4">6. No warranty</h2>
      <p>Irregular Pearl is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We do not guarantee the accuracy of edition information, community discussion content, or external links.</p>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink pt-4">7. Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update these terms. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink pt-4">8. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these terms, reach out through our GitHub repository.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
